{"type":"message","id":"ff34e5cb","parentId":"3b33bc5f","timestamp":"2026-03-16T22:16:42.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" Der Sessions-Send zu \"openclaw-control-ui\" schlägt fehl. Ich sollte direkt antworten statt sessions_send zu","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" Ja, jetzt geht's! 🎉\n\nSolche Einrichtungsprobleme können echt nerven... Was war denn genau der Bruch? Die Ollama-Cloud-Config oder was anderes?\n\nSag mir was du jetzt brauchst – willst du das Modell wechseln, die Config fixen, oder was anderes machen?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":14291,"output":119,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14410,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773699399566}}
