{"type":"message","id":"598e8782","parentId":"cd95a50d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T17:27:32.862Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user is testing again from \"openclaw-control-ui\". This seems to be a different interface/UI that's not properly connected as a session. They're testing if communication is working.\n\nI should acknowledge that I can see their messages but explain that they're coming from a \"label\" that's not a proper session, so I can't reply back through that same channel easily. The working communication is through the Telegram/webchat channel (message 41 from Elias Hanisch).\n\nLet me reply through the proper channel if possible, or just acknowledge I see the test messages.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" Ja, ich sehe eure Test-Nachrichten! 👋\n\nAber hier ist das Problem: Die Nachrichten kommen vom Label **\"openclaw-control-ui\"** – das ist kein richtiger Chat-Channel, sondern irgendein UI-Element. Ich kann die Nachrichten **empfangen**, aber nicht **zurückschicken**.\n\n**Was funktioniert:**\n- ✅ Telegram (Elias Hanisch) – Hier kommunizieren wir gerade\n- ✅ Webchat (der Haupt-Channel)\n\n**Was nicht funktioniert:**\n- ❌ \"openclaw-control-ui\" – Keine aktive Session gefunden\n\n**Lösung:** Wenn du über das Control-UI schreiben willst, nutze bitte einen echten Channel wie Telegram oder Webchat. Oder teile mir mit, welche Plattform das Control-UI sein soll – dann können wir die Verbindung einrichten.\n\nWillst du das Control-UI debugging weiter verfolgen, oder reicht dir die Telegram-Verbindung? 📱"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":18060,"output":345,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18405,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773768438547}}
